SummaryEnglish: At the pinnacle of immortality, proudly above the world, as long as I, Zu An, exist, there will be a heaven. Of the three million sword immortals in the world, all must bow their heads when they meet me. As the Keyboard Immortal, I must suppress all enemies in the world. Who dares to claim invincibility? Who dares to speak of being undefeated?
Aliases: Keyboard Crusader of the Mystical World
